  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of sofosbuvir /velpatasvir
      (SOF/VEL) fixed-dose combination (FDC) in participants with chronic hepatitis C virus (HCV)
      who have received a liver transplant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
